; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 296.664px 145.539px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 593px !important; height: 291px !important;"><canvas class="lt-highlighter__canvas" width="586" height="133" style="display: none; top: 46px !important; left: 0px !important;"></canvas></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-590411" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><p><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; background-color: var(--body_bg);"><br></span></p><p>For this next product we thought about the gift of roses, but without the wilted plant part. A great&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; background-color: var(--body_bg);">Valentine's Day choice instead of a flower bouquet is the&nbsp;</span><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; background-color: var(--body_bg);">iUNIK's 'Rose Galactomyces Synergy Serum'.</span></p><p><span style="background-color: var(--body_bg); color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit;"><br></span></p><p><span style="background-color: var(--body_bg); color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit;">This serum is the perfect option for those looking to give their skin a little extra love this Valentine's Day. Formulated with a combination of rose water and galactomyces ferment filtrate, this serum helps to </span><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; background-color: rgb(246, 217, 228);">brighten and nourish</span><span style="background-color: var(--body_bg); color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit;"> the skin while also </span><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; background-color: rgb(242, 216, 216);">r</span><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; background-color: rgb(246, 217, 228);">educing the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles</span><span style="background-color: var(--body_bg); color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit;">.</span></p><p><span style="background-color: var(--body_bg); color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit;"><br></span></p><p><span style="background-color: var(--body_bg); color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit;">Plus, its pink color adds a dash of romance to your skincare routine. Not to mention, the rose scent of the serum will make you feel like you're surrounded by a garden of roses, it's the perfect way to set the mood for a romantic evening.</span><br></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-4 gf_col-md-4 gf_col-sm-4 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1653642496901" data-id="1653642496901"><div data-label="Product" data-key="product" data-atomgroup="product" id="m-1660730398498" class="module-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-product" data-ver="3.1" data-id="1660730398498" style="min-height: auto;" data-assigned-ver="4"><div class="module" data-variant="auto" style="" data-current-variant="33116450619455">{% assign product = all_products['iunik-rose-galactomyces-synergy-serum'] %}{% unless product.empty?  %}{% form 'product', product, id: "", class: "AddToCartForm ", data-productid: product.id %}<input name="id" type="hidden" value="{{product.selected_or_first_available_variant.id}}" data-productid="{{product.id}}"><div data-index="1" class="item-content"><div class="module-wrap" id="m-1660730398498-0" data-id="1660730398498-0" data-label="(P) Image"><div class="module gf_module-center gf_module-center-lg gf_module--md gf_modul