 data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1660731840412" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1660731840412"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 593.328px !important; height: 358.25px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 296.664px 179.125px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 593px !important; height: 358px !important;"><canvas class="lt-highlighter__canvas" width="41" height="21" style="display: none; top: 68px !important; left: 31px !important;"></canvas></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-763350" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><p><br></p><p>Let's not forget Valentine's Day is the perfect excuse to vamp up your makeup routine.&nbsp;<span style="font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; background-color: var(--body_bg);">The Etude House's 'Dear Darling Water Tint' is a great way to add a pop of color to the lips. This adorable tint comes in 3 different romantic shades, including a beautiful pink hue that will make your lips look irresistible.&nbsp;</span></p><p><br></p><p>This water-based formula is lightweight and comfortable to wear, making it perfect for all-day wear.</p><p><br></p><p>Plus, it's infused with grapefruit extract, which is known for its <span style="background-color: rgb(246, 217, 228);">hydrating and nourishing</span> properties, ensuring that your lips will stay soft and healthy, not just on Valentine's Day, but all year round. The light and refreshing fruity scent of this lip tint makes it perfect for a romantic date.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-4 g